OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FRishi Sunak appoints ethics
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fadviser                    
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Rishi Sunak has appointed veteran      
OL,6, banker Sir Laurie Magnus as his new    
OL,7, adviser on ministerial behaviour.      
OL,9,FThe prime minister has been facing     
OL,10,Fpressure to fill the role, which has   
OL,11,Fbeen empty since the previous holder   
OL,12,Fquit six months ago.                   
OL,14,FSir Laurie, who also chairs Historic   
OL,15,FEngland, has been appointed to a       
OL,16,Fnon-renewable five-year term.          
OL,18,FHe will be responsible for advising Mr 
OL,19,FSunak on whether ministers are         
OL,20,Fcomplying with their conduct rulebook. 
